- Gemini

Alignment and Display in CSS
Text Alignment
    - text-align: Controls the horizontal alignment of text (left, center, right, justify).
Vertical Alignment
    - vertical-align: Sets vertical alignment of inline elements (top, middle, bottom).
Display Property
    - display: Determines how an element is displayed (block, inline, inline-block, flex).